summary: this mod contains skeleton replacements for use with, BBP armors/ mods that use BBP, Mystic Tails, 1HD weapons on back, daggers on pelvis back and many many others.
descriptionHtml:
[heading][center][color=orange]Description[/color][/center][/heading]
-just a simple skeleton replacer, allows use of the mods like mystic tails and DSpSoB with other mods that replace the skeleton.

-for now i am no longer taking requests

-DSpSoB and ATTT will not work together because the esp's conflict. as far as i know they can be made to work together by editing the esp's in CK but i do not know how.

-[i][b][color=red]DO NOT[/color][/b][/i] upload any of my packs without my permission. out of respect for the original authors if you want to upload any of them you MUST get my permission i suggest also getting the permission from the original authors to use their assets as well.

-[i][b][color=red]I WILL NOT[/color][/b][/i] do any combos for XP32's Maximum Skeleton. it is a major pain to see anything, i just cannot see what i am doing to work on them.

please list what you would like it makes it easier to read
--------example---------
4 pack (male female beast)
-TBBP
-Perfect 3-2
-RR - Realistic
-DSpSoB WOH
-SWP dual daggers on ankles
-WPWQ


-Mystic tails is not required for any of the skeletons that are compatible with it, it is completely optional, only thing you will notice is the different aura if you use detect life

-ALL SKELETONS WILL WORK WITH CBBEV3, CBBEV3M, UNP, UNPB, ADEC AND VANILLA BODIES. as for LB or other bodies im not sure, if you use these let me know if they work with them and i will fixs this. if you are using UNP/UNPB and have clipping issues with WPWQ let me know and ill get another version up.

[i][b][color=green]PLEASE ENDORSE[/color][/b][/i]
the more endorsements, positive feedback and screenshots i receive will help me to stay motivated enough to keep this going. right now i just do not have the motivation and ambition to keep doing this. i will still take requests but i will only be updating once a week usually on a saturday. im sorry for the waiting/inconvenience.

[i][b][color=red]NOTICE[/color][/b][/i]
anyone who dislikes the Bolt quiver placement check out EvilDeadAsh34's
Closer Quivers and Longer Arrows mod he has a fix for it which moves the quiver closer to the body without modifying the skeleton

[i][b][color=yellow]WARNING 1[/color][/b][/i]
when using any skeleton with DSpSoB any weapon that has only one placement or no shield spot will be on the ground.


[heading][center][color=orange]GLOSSARY[/color][/center][/heading]
-1HD - 1HD weapons on back
-SWP-DOA - skyrim weapon positioning - dagger on ankle
-WPWQ - well placed weapons and quiver
-RR - realistic ragdolls
-WOTS - way of the sword
-NMDS - no more dangling swords
-DOPB - dagger on pelvis back (single dagger)
-ATTT - Armed to the Teeth
-DSpSoB WOB- Dual Sheath plus Shield on Back Weapons on back (swords, daggers, staffs and shield on back )
-BBSB - Better Body Scale Beasts
-DSpSoB WoH - Dual Sheath plus Shields on Back Weapons on hips (shields and staffs on back swords and daggers on hips)
-TBBP - tender breast and butt physics


[heading][center][color=orange]INSTALL[/color][/center][/heading]
for manual install place the skeletons in the appropriate folders in
C:/Program Files (x86)/Steam/steamapps/common/skyrim/Data/meshes/actors/character

-always install the skeletons last, over write if asked.


[heading][center][color=orange]MODS[/color][/center][/heading]
this is a list of mods which i can make combinations of.
all skeletons that have BBP will work with CHSBHC or any body that uses BBP
if there are any you would like that i dont have let me know and i will see what i can do

-Mystic tails
-Way of the Sword - Skyrim Katana Revised
-DSpSoB - Dual Sheath plus Shields on Back
-Stacked Against Gravity Body and Armors with BBP and Scaling
-Daggers on pelvis back [color=orange]SUSPENDED unti i can get a chance to fix it[/color]
-Hide Bow and Quiver

-DOA - Dual Daggers on Ankles.
-Better Male Skeletons
-Chesko's Belt-Fastened Quivers - Skeleton Replacer - frostfall
